<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2009-12-15</DATELINE><TITLE>A “One Health” Approach to Address Emerging Zoonoses: The HALI Project in Tanzania</TITLE><BODY>Jonna Mazet and colleagues describe their work in the Tanzania-based HALI Project, which adopts the “One Health” approach to address emerging zoonoses and that recognizes the interconnectedness of human, animal, and environmental health.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>